&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a BIM Associate I to join our team in a fully remote capacity. In this role, you will support the design and modeling of architectural and engineering projects, focusing on creating Onboarding permit drawings, working with Revit models, and assisting in schematic and tender design tasks. If you’re passionate about BIM and eager to grow your skills in a remote setting, we want to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
