&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At CloudKitchens, we’re building the infrastructure that powers the future of food. We acquire, transform, and operate real estate assets globally—turning underutilized properties into high-performance commercial kitchen facilities for thousands of restaurant partners.&amp;nbsp;Our Real Estate, Expansion, and Operations teams work at lightning speed to identify, acquire, and launch properties that enable operators to grow with lower upfront costs and minimal complexity.&lt;/p&gt;
