&lt;p&gt;As a Real Estate Recruiter, you will play a critical role in scaling the teams responsible for site sourcing, acquisitions, underwriting, expansion, construction, and asset management. You’ll recruit the dealmakers, operators, and execution-focused builders who will drive CloudKitchens’ next phase of global real estate growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
