&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communicator able to build trust with senior stakeholders and candidates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly organized, detail-oriented, and data-driven, with the ability to thrive in a fast-paced, execution-heavy environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mission-first mindset—comfortable operating with urgency and extreme ownership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
